  <brief_title>Antimycotic Prophylaxis in Pediatric Patients Following Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety, Feasibility and Efficacy of Caspofungin Versus Liposomal Amphotericin B as Antifungal Prophylaxis Following Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation in Pediatric Patients - a Retrospective Phase I/II Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
