  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pediatric patients are at high risk to acquire mycotic infections following allogeneic bone
      marrow transplantation. In the present retrospective analysis we assess the safety and
      efficacy of different regimens in antimycotic prophylaxis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
